	  directory names. Thanks to Tom Lowery, <tlowery@dsioj.dla.mil>.
	* t/threadm.t (MyChild): Use of alarm() now depends on a working
	  alarm() function. (Not working under Win32.) Thanks to Tom
	  Lowery, <tlowery@dsioj.dla.mil>

